            "spec": "05",
            "capability": "OSFP Heatsink",
            "detail": "Supporting optical transceivers from 800G up to 3.2T, Cofan's solutions are also adaptable to both air- and liquid-cooled systems, ensuring efficient thermal performance across a wide range of deployment scenarios."
